Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:48.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found them easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:54.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find anything if you look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:57.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like coming back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:06.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, wasn't it Rio-senpai's turn to manage the garden today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:09.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had something to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been half a year since Kanata arrived at the fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her skills have improved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:31.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher is good after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:40.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we don't even need earplugs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:49.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better for you to stay in the city during winter, Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not die so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:04.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living here on the mountain alone for 50 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:14.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Down. Down. Down. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:18.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally looks like it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you finish the rest on your own, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:22.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a cup of tea then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:36.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The military chronicle should be here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata said that she wants to know more about Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:00.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, if it's not there, I have no idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:02.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san may have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask her later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:24.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Iliya is the elder daughter of the present King Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:31.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told you before that she's a famous tanker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:35.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus-san said something last time, if she was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:41.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She died around 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:49.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess had been allocated to Team Guardian...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:54.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was also responsible for publicising the National Prestige and had to travel all around the Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:05:00.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she was on her way to a certain city, she died while trying to rescue a kid who'd fallen into a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I felt a bit relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though this is only a rumour...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san and... Well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, it's Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:44.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san ... err... has come with Yuuko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:49.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan is the daughter of Martin-san and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, a lady named Jakotto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jakotto-san is living on the mountain alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:00.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some vegetables from her as well, at the market...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:04.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You said that the pickled food was nice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was made from Jakotto-san's vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:14.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jakotto-san disappeared recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're worried since her health is not that good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:23.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that she's living in a remote area in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help them. Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Iliya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:44.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To improve the relationship between the two countries, she married the Emperor of Traditional Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she would've been the third Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The third! The third Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed like nothing but a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:07:00.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After she died, the marriage was cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:05.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And war went on until the beginning of this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh cool... We've finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A house under construction...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:36.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Yuuko went to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:46.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin should be proud of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really nice house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:54.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I built this house myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the one over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:03.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:09.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's in a city far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:14.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am preparing the house so he can have a place to live once he's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can live comfortably with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish building the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:38.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When will your son come back, Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He will come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter will come even sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better leave the mountain before the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:55.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I have to finish building that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:09:00.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave this place before I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:00.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no joking matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to prepare for the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The firewood?  How about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have not prepared yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:13.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're worrying about me, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stubborn old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are really alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I be doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:42.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not honest enough with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:51.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Why did you show me the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also mentioned in the regular liaison...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:02.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Roman Army in the Eastern area is moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? For Jakotto-obaasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Please take these with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:35.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how the peace conference is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if Princess Iliya was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:51.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way... Martin, I heard that Princess Iliya had a younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your change, 4 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:11:00.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that she's an illegitimate child of the King and thus her existence was not publicised...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:04.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that she is of the third heirship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.68,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. The younger sister you just mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:28.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the village you were born in look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a normal village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:41.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are farms. There are a lot of cows and lambs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there aren't very many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a nice place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents are nice too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:58.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the place where Senpai grew up look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:05.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up in a place not too far from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are beautiful forests and lakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:15.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived with my mother in such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:20.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The days were simple and boring. Nothing surprising ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:28.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only pleasure was the visit of my older step-sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:33.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She came to play with me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was prestigious and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was easygoing about her fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:47.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who taught me the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:51.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was too gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her gentleness got her killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:00.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first arrived at the city, I thought it was a labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my way, and finally, I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I reached the goal line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:21.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I soon realised that this was just an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I always get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I love to be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting lost is nothing bad! Even if it is an impasse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:46.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you because of this, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:56.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I'm really envious of you, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:05.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could be as honest as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:26.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you worrying about a person like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:35.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you resemble my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:40.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember having a daughter as pretty as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born from a forbidden love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had been waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting for a man who might not even come once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:56.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she died in this misfortune and misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:01.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know she was miserable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:11.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that person promised to come back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised that he would come and take me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:17.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What else is there for me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:28.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were anything else, I might have done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:39.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember that I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:45.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The memory of him is still in my heart. And so is the hope that we will see each other again one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought it was getting cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:28.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was snowing as well, when I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:42.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Madam was young, Seize was a nice place to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:04.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She fell in love with the honorable son of a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:14.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, she was pregnant with his child. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:18.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That young master was already married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:24.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As luck would have it though, his wife was sterile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:29.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the young master went back to his hometown with her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:37.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And promised to take her with him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:10.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to my age, it's common to think that...  If, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Jakotto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:18.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Life... is to lose repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to gain something to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:29.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the more happiness you have gained, the more terrible it is to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:39.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, with the memory of happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:44.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the memories are with us... We can keep living...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:53.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way... This may not be a good time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found it. The photo of Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Felicia... It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was around 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:05.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was taken when the Princess came to Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Shuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:23.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that my parents actually wanted me to get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And inherit the family property.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:33.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I was fascinated by the sound of the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I could never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:42.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Iliya-san, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:47.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya-san's music rings in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:58.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we met each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, I used this city as an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:08.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, in the beginning, I didn't care about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that I would leave one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:18.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I truly want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the same sense, I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:30.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to do it, and there are things only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far apart we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The music will ring out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:51.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The music will ring out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:55.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And... reach... one's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:22:02.88,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata... Was I a good senpai to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:06.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:26.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, Rio-senpai left us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:37.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And left that amazingly beautiful sound of the skies ringing in my heart.
